    {
      "label": "Execution Protocol (one plugin at a time)",
      "file_type": "rationale",
      "source_file": "PRD.md",
      "source_location": "\u00a71",
      "source_url": null,
      "captured_at": null,
      "author": null,
      "contributor": null,
      "rationale": "One plugin fully finished at a time, DSP core before GUI, offline test harness catches math bugs pre-GUI. If blocked >90 min descope to docs/DEFERRED.md and move on: a working suite with gaps beats a stalled perfect plugin. Toolchain breakage takes priority over everything.",
      "id": "prd_execution_protocol",
      "community": 0,
      "norm_label": "execution protocol (one plugin at a time)"
    },
    {
      "label": "suite-core (shared lib crate)",
      "file_type": "concept",
      "source_file": "PRD.md",
      "source_location": "\u00a72",
      "source_url": null,
      "captured_at": null,
      "author": null,
      "contributor": null,
      "rationale": "Shared DSP (filters, delay lines, oversampling, STFT, pitch detector, grain engine, FDN, LUFS meter), egui theme/widgets, bus layer, and preset save/load live in one workspace crate so every plugin after the first builds faster and the suite looks like one product family.",
      "id": "prd_suite_core",
      "community": 1,
      "norm_label": "suite-core (shared lib crate)"
    },
    {
      "label": "The Bus (cross-plugin shared state)",
      "file_type": "concept",
      "source_file": "PRD.md",
      "source_location": "\u00a73",
      "source_url": null,
      "captured_at": null,
      "author": null,
      "contributor": null,
      "rationale": "Rust statics are per-DLL and FL can bridge plugins out of process, so two tiers: (1) same-DLL static Mutex<Registry> for OVERSEER Node+Master exported from one .vst3; (2) cross-DLL named shared memory (memmap2 slab in %TEMP%\\qeynos-bus) with per-slot seqlocks and block-counter heartbeats. No locks or allocation in the audio callback. Honest constraints: block-size granularity only, and Master param overrides bypass host automation/undo.",
      "id": "prd_the_bus",
      "community": 5,
      "norm_label": "the bus (cross-plugin shared state)"
    },
